---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
// Dedicated disclaimer architecture (Decision 4 / ADR-006). Product, not just copy.
---
<BaseLayout title="Disclaimers" description="Important disclaimers: Rocco equips and never diagnoses, emergency guidance, and the limits of this service.">
  <section class="container" style="padding:48px 20px 64px; max-width:760px">
    <h1>Disclaimers</h1>
    <h2>Rocco equips, he never diagnoses</h2>
    <p>Rocco gives you general understanding and the right questions to ask. He does not diagnose problems, does not guarantee causes, and is not a substitute for a licensed professional.</p>
    <h2>Educational, not professional advice</h2>
    <p>Everything here is for general information only. It is not professional, licensed, legal, medical, or engineering advice. Always hire a qualified, licensed pro for actual work and inspections.</p>
    <div class="disclaimer">
      <strong>In an emergency, stop and get help now.</strong> If you smell gas, see sparking or smoke, suspect carbon monoxide, or have active flooding or anything structurally unsafe &mdash; leave if needed and call 911 or your local utility immediately. Do not wait to ask Rocco.
    </div>
    <h2>Local listings</h2>
    <p>Nearby businesses are sourced from third parties such as Google and shown as nearby options, not endorsements or paid rankings. We never fabricate reviews, ratings, or counts.</p>
    <h2>HVAC partner pilot</h2>
    <p>For HVAC in the Jersey Shore launch area, Rocco may offer to connect you with a managed trusted partner. This is optional and consent-based. In this early phase it is a stub and may not result in a real connection yet.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
